<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>I REMEMBER CALVARY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ei puihna chengah zui ingka,
 Amah muon dan chuh ka hetai;
 Kei ading ahi, ka hechien,
 Amah A thii Kalvari-ah.

[V2]
 Sun leh zanin Isu'n ei pui,
 Ama'n lamtawn in ei pui ding;
 Kei dinga Guol dik pen ahi,
 Kalvari ka hezing zing hi.

[V3]
 2. A thupiek haw ka kipahpih,
 A khuta ei puih ka nuom hi;
 A deihlam kei dingin a phai,
 Kalvari-ah thi'n A thiensak.

[V4]
 3. Lung lau loin ka chieh zel hi,
 Hukdampa a nai, nuom ka sai;
 Nikhat tei Amah chuh mu'ng ka,
 Kalvari Isu chuh ka Guol.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>265</hymn_number>
</song>